{"tid":398870,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一定要愛自己","createTime":"2017-09-13T13:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T18:57:41.000Z","uid":68304,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50a7348d1bf89b587c293fe097e3bf801f65b33a","tid":398870,"uid":68304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"係呢個收兵，玩弄人感情當水飲既環境下<br />\n大家千祈唔好對人付出所有感情<br />\n要保護好自己，對自己好，其他全部都係廢話<br />\n不論巴定絲，溝唔到既咪算。<br />\n自己食野既時候食好d貴d，買靚衫靚鞋俾自己<br />\n識多d朋友，令自己生活更加美好。<br />\n唔好咁易動情，要變得冷漠。<br />\n<br />\n祝大家唔會再受傷。"},{"pid":"e347c8c708a0b8e3b8e0dc7b25859344f0556a93","tid":398870,"uid":143307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:26:50.000Z","msg":"認同你<br />\n不過有時候 自己付出了真心還是得不到回報固然傷心<br />\n但是起碼自己也不會有遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b70870dedf6c6a9bc389c0c30d375bc6614c6ac","tid":398870,"uid":68304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同你<br />\n不過有時候 自己付出了真心還是得不到回報固然傷心<br />\n但是起碼自己也不會有遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己心目中單方面遺憾 不了"},{"pid":"259e915b1cb432ac323979e06eb399e5f7b612ae","tid":398870,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"哦，收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得被人玩弄感情先算"},{"pid":"2180c456e650303ce3f9e8e8538a3bd56a1e10c2","tid":398870,"uid":68304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦，收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得被人玩弄感情先算</blockquote><br />\n冇咪將d時間不斷投資其他野到<br />\n豐富自己人生 好快就會有收穫"},{"pid":"fce16bf46253e579a401b55fcb5f7145e83d3f76","tid":398870,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"c893619e1fa3289f813226fdea830f08f8da5d34","tid":398870,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s